                <ul class="gs-checklist">
                    <li>@T("V Supabase musí existovať SYSTEM so správnym sn_number.", "Supabase must contain a SYSTEM row with the correct sn_number.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Do firmware nastav PROJECT_URL, API_KEY a SN_NUMBER. SN_NUMBER je spojovací kľúč medzi meničom, tabuľkami a používateľom.", "Set PROJECT_URL, API_KEY, and SN_NUMBER in firmware. SN_NUMBER is the linking key between inverter, tables, and user.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Pre zber dát over zápis do PV_INFORMATION, GRID_INFORMATION, BATTERY_INFORMATION a STATISTICAL_INFORMATION.", "For data collection verify writes into PV_INFORMATION, GRID_INFORMATION, BATTERY_INFORMATION, and STATISTICAL_INFORMATION.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Ak node riadi WattRouter, over aj WATTROUTER_INFO.", "If the node controls WattRouter, also verify WATTROUTER_INFO.")</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="gs-wiring-card">
                <h3>@T("3. Silová časť", "3. Power control side")</h3>
                <ul class="gs-checklist">
                    <li>@T("Použi zero-crossing SSR relé pre AC odporovú záťaž, nie náhodné DC SSR. Príklad: Carlo Gavazzi RGC1A23D15KKE približne pre 3 kW na fázu alebo RGS1A23D25KKEDIN približne pre 2 kW na fázu.", "Use zero-crossing SSR relays for AC resistive loads, not random DC SSRs. Example: Carlo Gavazzi RGC1A23D15KKE for roughly 3 kW per phase or RGS1A23D25KKEDIN for roughly 2 kW per phase.")</li>
                    <li>@T("SSR výstupy zapájaj cez vhodné istenie a chladič. Silovú časť nech robí osoba s elektrotechnickou kvalifikáciou.", "Connect SSR outputs with proper protection and heatsinking. The mains side should be handled by a qualified electrician.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Modulovaný SSR výstup používaj na plynulé smerovanie prebytku, pevné SSR stupne na dopnutie výkonu po krokoch.", "Use the modulated SSR output for smooth surplus routing and fixed SSR stages for step-based power increases.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Termostatický vstup používaj ako bezpečnostnú podmienku pre ohrev vody.", "Use the thermostat input as a safety condition for water heating.")</li>
                    <li>@T("Pri wallboxe alebo analógovom regulátore najprv nastav minimálny a maximálny výkon zariadenia, až potom povoľ automatiku.", "For wallbox or analog control, first set the device minimum and maximum power, then enable automation.")</li>
                </ul>
            </article>

            <article class="gs-wiring-card">
                <h3>@T("4. Overenie pred ostrou prevádzkou", "4. Verification before live operation")</h3>
